sequenceDiagram
    participant APP as Go 接入服务
    participant R as Redis
    participant MQ as RocketMQ
    participant SC as Reservation 扫描器
    participant C as 订单消费者
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    APP->>R: 预占成功
    R-->>APP: reservation_id
    Note over APP: 发送 MQ 前进程宕机
    SC->>R: 扫描超时的 RESERVED reservation
    SC->>MQ: 使用同一 message_id 补发
    MQ->>C: 投递订单创建消息
    C->>PG: Inbox 幂等事务
    PG-->>C: 订单创建成功
    C->>R: reservation → ORDER_CREATED
